{"tid":2031554,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【港台】《零距離科學》大麻兩面睇","createTime":"2020-05-23T13:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T15:26:58.000Z","uid":200165,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"53d0ffe58ff519f5751dffb0de46737fd201b0ec","tid":2031554,"uid":200165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:04:40.000Z","msg":"【港台】《零距離科學》大麻兩面睇 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/sciencewithyou/episode/627497?fbclid=IwAR0VP_hjv7UTiK4FbVe8vlA2PREMq7Tq3ZPkGDhaVDR3YfqazQXwk24fBgs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fsciencewithyou%2Fepisode%2F627497%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0VP_hjv7UTiK4FbVe8vlA2PREMq7Tq3ZPkGDhaVDR3YfqazQXwk24fBgs&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=3a266692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/sciencewithyou/episode/627497?fbclid=IwAR0VP_hjv7UTiK4FbVe8vlA2PREMq7Tq3ZPkGDhaVDR3YfqazQXwk24fBgs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大麻兩面睇<br />\n<br />\n大麻是世上其中一種最古老和最具爭議性的藥物，而這種藥物現正面臨一個非常特別的時刻。攝製團隊調查了最新的醫學和科學研究，找出大麻對大腦和人體的影響。<br />\n自2018年11月1日起，醫學用大麻在英國正式合法化，不過在實際上仍然存在很多爭議。急症室醫生賈偉德．阿卜杜莫尼希望找出大麻是否對病人有利，還是會帶來傷害。"},{"pid":"b0d99a468edf87dcf1185f00d58ce04b1e99ff56","tid":2031554,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"好波！"},{"pid":"058894a060496e325db5a1606a58ac0f4ad769ed","tid":2031554,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:26:58.000Z","msg":"唔知教育局點睇？"}]}